{"tid":1286959,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"李小龍名言 –「不要祈求安逸的人生，祈求擁有撐過艱難的力量。」","createTime":"2019-07-05T04:27:27.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-05T04:35:27.000Z","uid":269098,"like":9,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"c241980d7bcf19a7103a864b19529a3d788e4d7c","tid":1286959,"uid":269098,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:27:27.000Z","msg":"啱啱做research睇到呢句（如題）<br />\n建議大家參考一下已故武術家李小龍的名言，可能有幫助：<br />\n<br />\n<em>Focus is the key to success</em><br />\n「專注是成功的關鍵。」<br />\n<br />\n<em>The purpose of life is to faithfully develop its potential and complete itself.</em><br />\n「人生的目的在於忠實地發展自身的潛能,完成自我。」<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">(後加：但不要自我毀滅）</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<em>Knowing is not enough, we must apply. Willing is not enough, we must do.</em><br />\n「知道不足夠，要應用。願意不足夠，要行動。」<br />\n<br />\n<em>I&rsquo;m not in this world to live up to your expectations and you&rsquo;re not in this world to live up to mine.</em><br />\n「我活在這世界裹不是要符合你的期望，而你亦不是。」<br />\n<br />\n<em>Real living is living for others.</em><br />\n「真正的活著是為別人而活。」<br />\n<br />\n原文網址：<br />\n<a href=\"https://kknews.cc/history/oopaj3q.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fkknews.cc%2Fhistory%2Foopaj3q.html&d=J%2B7a%2FypYnyyex2M81OHxVcZCnWmYDHHppvVe94ioujI%3D&h=9e99721a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://kknews.cc/history/oopaj3q.html</a><br />\n<a href=\"http://www.bilquote.com/files/b/blee/blee2.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.bilquote.com%2Ffiles%2Fb%2Fblee%2Fblee2.html&d=J%2B7a%2FypYnyyex2M81OHxVcZCnWmYDHHppvVe94ioujI%3D&h=7576805a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.bilquote.com/files/b/blee/blee2.html</a>"},{"pid":"ac3b5afd3da3a09a0bf3f6110ca1c3cb8bf62c7d","tid":1286959,"uid":211461,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-07-05T04:29:09.000Z","msg":"Be water my friend"},{"pid":"72689b48cb341a8d50eec15bb7a